            <h1 class="req-title">College Educational Assistance</h1>
            <div>
                <p class="req-definition">A form of assistance given to eligible students to help defray school expenses and/or cost of sending students/children to school such as school fees, supplies, projects, allowance and other related expenses.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="req-list">
                <h2 class="req-list-title">List of Requirements</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><a class="" href="/college-assistance/form">General Intake Sheet (Register and Download)</a></li>
                    <li>Personal Letter of Request Addressed to the Mayor.</li>
                    <li>Copy of Registration Form - for the current semester as proof they are enrolled (bring original and 1 photocopy).</li>
                    <li>Certificate of Grades from the Previous Semester Duly Signed by the College Registrar with dry seal (1 original)</li>
                    <li>Barangay Clearance with dry seal (1 original)</li>
                    <li>Certificate of Indigency (1 original)</li>
                    <li>Validated School ID (Bring 1 photocopy)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="/college-assistance/form">
                <button class="btn btn-primary">Proceed</button>
            </a>
